title: Turkey Bowling with Jesus Fuego
itunes:title: Turkey Bowling with Jesus Fuego
description: We're bowling with Turkey's, hanging with the "miracle man" Jesus Fuego, and saying good bye to Twinkies. We light up Jesus Fuego's Edition de Familiar, and Originals; Origen Originals, Origen Maduro and Sangre de Toro (Blood of the Bull).
